#: ../../../prop_sf/INSTALL_OBJECT_NAME.rst:2
msgid "INSTALL_OBJECT_NAME"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../prop_sf/INSTALL_OBJECT_NAME.rst:6
msgid ""
"Set the installed object name (without the object extension) of the source "
"file. An empty string value disables custom object naming. The value must be "
"a relative path, and may not include special directory components (e.g., ``.."
"``)."
msgstr ""
"設定來源檔案的已安裝目標名稱（不含副檔名）。空字串值會停用自訂目標命名。該值"
"必須是相對路徑，且不得包含特殊目錄組件（例如 ``..``）。"

#: ../../../prop_sf/INSTALL_OBJECT_NAME.rst:11
msgid ""
"Note that the object name might not be used as-is in some :prop_tgt:"
"`INSTALL_OBJECT_NAME_STRATEGY` strategies.  It may be changed as the "
"strategy requires to fulfill its goals."
msgstr ""
"請注意，在某些 :prop_tgt:`INSTALL_OBJECT_NAME_STRATEGY` 策略中，目標名稱可能"
"不會按原樣使用。它可能會根據策略的需要進行更改以實現其目標。"

#: ../../../prop_sf/INSTALL_OBJECT_NAME.rst:15
msgid ""
"This property supports :manual:`generator expressions <cmake-generator-"
"expressions(7)>`."
msgstr "此屬性支援 :manual:`生成器表達式 <cmake-generator-expressions(7)>`。"

#: ../../../prop_sf/INSTALL_OBJECT_NAME.rst:19
msgid ""
"No collision resistance within a target is performed by CMake. When using "
"this property, collisions must be avoided in the project code. CMake has a "
"number of source files it generates that also create object files that may "
"collide with a given custom name. These include:"
msgstr ""
"CMake 不會對目標內的名稱衝突進行防護。使用此屬性時，必須在專案程式碼中避免衝"
"突。CMake 會產生一些也會建立目標檔的來源檔案，這些檔案可能與給定的自訂名稱衝"
"突。其中包括："

#: ../../../prop_sf/INSTALL_OBJECT_NAME.rst:24
msgid "Generated PCH source files (``cmake_pch``)"
msgstr "產生的 PCH 來源檔案 (``cmake_pch``)"

#: ../../../prop_sf/INSTALL_OBJECT_NAME.rst:25
msgid "Generated Unity compilation files (``unity_...``)"
msgstr "產生的 Unity 編譯檔案 (``unity_...``)"

#: ../../../prop_sf/INSTALL_OBJECT_NAME.rst:26
msgid "Qt autogen sources (``moc_compilations.cpp``)"
msgstr "Qt autogen 來源 (``moc_compilations.cpp``)"
